Private ChairJCATSRS As Recordset
Private criteria As String

Private Sub Detail_Format(Cancel As Integer, FormatCount As Integer)
  'On Error GoTo suberror
  Dim chnum As Integer
  chnum = IIf(IsNull(Me.tbCHAIRNUM), 0, Me.tbCHAIRNUM)
  Me.tbJCATS = ""
  Me.tbJCATS.FontBold = False
  If chnum > 0 Then
     criteria = "SELECT JCAT FROM JUDGETYPES WHERE " & _
             "CHAIRNUM = " & chnum & " ORDER BY JCAT"
  Else
    criteria = "SELECT JCAT FROM JUDGETYPES WHERE " & _
             "CHAIRNUM = null ORDER BY JCAT"
  End If
  Set ChairJCATSRS = CurrentDb().OpenRecordset(criteria, dbOpenDynaset)
  With ChairJCATSRS
    If .EOF Then
      If Me.CSt = "A" And Me.TC = "P" Then
         Me.tbJCATS.FontBold = True
         Me.tbJCATS = "CAUTION: ACTIVE," & vbCrLf & _
                      "PRIMARY Judge" & vbCrLf & _
                      "with NO JCATs"
      Else ' not an active primary chair
         If Me.CSt = "A" And Me.TC <> "P" Then ' Active other (Assistant or honorary)
              If Me.TC = "H" Then
                Me.tbJCATS = "Honorary Chair" & vbCrLf
              Else
                If Me.TC = "A" Then
                  Me.tbJCATS = "Assistant Chair" & vbCrLf
                Else
                  If Me.TC = "M" Then  ' Master chair
                    Me.tbJCATS = "Master Chair" & vbCrLf
                  Else
                    Me.tbJCATS = "Chairtype" & Me.TC & vbCrLf
                  End If
                End If
              End If
              'Me.tbJCATS = Me.tbJCATS & "Assisting Chair " & Me.Ast & vbCrLf
              Me.tbJCATS = Me.tbJCATS & "Assisting: " & vbCrLf
           ' add name here later
              Dim rs2 As Recordset
              criteria = "SELECT Chairs.CHAIRNUM, Persons.FNAME, Persons.LNAME, Persons.MI " & _
              "FROM Persons RIGHT JOIN (Judges RIGHT JOIN Chairs ON Judges.JUN = Chairs.JUN) ON " & _
              "Persons.PID = Judges.PID;"
              Set rs2 = CurrentDb().OpenRecordset(criteria, dbOpenDynaset)
              With rs2
              .FindFirst "CHAIRNUM = " & IIf(IsNull(Me.Ast), 0, Me.Ast)
              If .NoMatch Then
                 If Me.TC = "M" Then  ' Master chair needs no Me.ast - helps all
                   Me.tbJCATS = Me.tbJCATS & "ALL Chairs"
                 Else
                    Me.tbJCATS = Me.tbJCATS & "ERROR! fix problem"
                 End If
              Else
                 Me.tbJCATS = Me.tbJCATS & !FNAME & " " & !LNAME
              End If
              rs2.Close
              End With
         Else '  Not a primary active and not assistant active
              Me.tbJCATS = "Inactive This Year" & vbCrLf & _
                            "No Assigns"
         End If
      End If
    Else
      Me.tbJCATS.FontBold = True
      .MoveFirst
      Do While Not .EOF
         Me.tbJCATS = Me.tbJCATS & !JCAT & ", "
        .MoveNext
      Loop
    End If
    .Close
  End With
  ' Check out the Assistants - each that is active should have an active
  ' primary Chair listed in ASSISTING
  If Me.TC <> "P" And Me.CSt = "A" Then  ' and ACTIVE  ASSISTANT '
    Dim failed As Boolean
    failed = False
    If IsNull(Me.Ast) Or Me.Ast = 0 Then
       If Me.TC <> "M" Then
         failed = True
       End If
    Else
      Dim rs As Recordset
      Set rs = CurrentDb().OpenRecordset("Chairs", dbOpenDynaset)
      With rs
        .FindFirst "CHAIRNUM = " & Me.Ast
        If .NoMatch Then
          failed = True  ' listed chair is not even in table
        Else
          If !Type <> "P" Or (!Type = "P" And (IsNull(!STATUS) Or _
                              !STATUS <> "A")) Then
            failed = True
          End If
        End If
        .Close
      End With
    End If
    If failed = True Then
      Me.tbJCATS.FontBold = True
      Me.tbJCATS = "CAUTION: Active" & vbCrLf & _
                    "Assistant, NOT" & vbCrLf & _
                    "Assisting ACTIVE " & vbCrLf & _
                    "PRIMARY CHAIR?"
    End If
  End If
  Exit Sub
SubError:
  MsgBox Err.Description
End Sub
